1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,483
Once upon a time, a young scholar lived in a small village.

2
00:00:03,783 --> 00:00:07,452
Every day he studied, reading books under the old oak tree.

3
00:00:07,752 --> 00:00:12,164
One day, he decided to travel to the royal court for the examination.

4
00:00:12,464 --> 00:00:16,504
After a long journey, the scholar finally arrived at the castle.

5
00:00:16,804 --> 00:00:20,055
Standing before the palace, he marveled at its grandeur.

6
00:00:20,355 --> 00:00:23,977
The great hall was filled with scholars from across the kingdom.

7
00:00:24,277 --> 00:00:28,410
The scholar poured all his effort into writing the examination.

8
00:00:28,710 --> 00:00:31,311
At last, the day of the results arrived.

9
00:00:31,611 --> 00:00:35,605
The scholar earned the king's favor and became the pride of his village.

10
00:00:35,905 --> 00:00:40,410
And so, the scholar became a trusted court advisor serving the people.
